values: hand back [phrasal verb]hand (something) back or hand back (something): to return (something) by handing it to someone退回；交还He handed the letter back (to her) without reading it.他看都没看就把信退回（给她）。The clerk handed back my credit card.营业员把信用卡交还给我。 hand
